# Authors

## Original author

- **Robert Bajzat** &lt;rbajzat@freemail.hu&gt; — creator and author of the
  Thinlet GUI toolkit (2002–2005). All of the library code in
  `thinlet-core/src/main/java/thinlet/Thinlet.java` and
  `FrameLauncher.java`, the demos, the drafts, and the original
  documentation are his work. Original site: https://thinlet.sourceforge.net/

The LGPL 2.1 copyright headers in the source files are preserved verbatim.
This fork adds no new copyright claim over the original code.

## Modernization fork

- **C. Bartlett** &lt;cbartlett@nomixer.com&gt; — modernization-fork maintainer
  (nomixer). Responsible for the Maven build, tooling, tests, CI, and
  cross-JDK packaging in this repository. Not an author of the original
  Thinlet library.
